<p class="">—it is most important that the Economic Secretary should make it clear how he expects to implement the vigorous pursuit of the Government in these matters and, above all, how they are to effect a real and proper balance in the various elements affected in the implementation of the White Paper.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
